nhiu block ang cng mt trang, cc block xut hin v vic to ni dung tr nn d dng hn, cn c cc gii php  lm cho ni dung phc tp d iu hng. Ch  xem danh sch (List View) l cch tt nht  chuyn gia cc lp ni dung v cc block lng nhau. V Ch  xem danh sch cung cp cho bn ci nhn tng quan v tt c cc khi trong ni dung ca bn, gi y bn c th iu hng nhanh chng n khi chnh xc m bn cn.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2021/07/about-pattern-suggestions.png\" alt=\"Xem trc mu block\" width=\"370\" height=\"200\" /><figcaption>Xem trc mu block trc khi thm vo</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Chuyn Widget thnh Block</h2>\n\n\n\n<p>y l mt cp nht ng ch , chuyn giao din Widget bn mc nh sang giao din trnh chnh sa Block. Trong trng hp giao din khng tng thch, bn nn chuyn ngc li bng cch ci plugin <a href=\"https://vi.wordpress.org/plugins/classic-widgets/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Classic Widgets</a>.</p>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2021/07/about-widgets-blocks.png\" alt=\"Block widget mi\" width=\"356\" height=\"267\" /><figcaption>Block cho php nhng widget mi</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://kweb.vn/wp-content/uploads/2021/07/widget-area.png\" alt=\"Khu vc widget area mi trong WordPress 5.8\" class=\"wp-image-901\" width=\"459\" height=\"216\" /><figcaption>Giao din Widget Area mi</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Hin th bi vit trong Block Editor</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2021/07/about-query-loop.png\" alt=\"Block cho php chn danh sch bi vit\" width=\"385\" height=\"305\" /><figcaption>Block cho php chn danh sch bi vit</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Trong phin bn WordPress 5.8, mt trong nhng vn  au u l cch hin th block danh sch bi vit  c x l. Trnh son tho block cung cp mt block Query Loop cho php la chn nhiu ty chnh t s lng bi vit, hin th danh mc, ngy thng cho ti b sung pagination. Kh thun tin nhng cng vn l c bn v cn nhiu hn cho mt website.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cu trc trang tng th</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://i1.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2021/07/about-list-view.png\" alt=\"Sp xp layer trong WordPress\" width=\"388\" height=\"303\" /><figcaption>Sp xp layer trong WordPress</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>C th bn cn mt trang landing n gin, nhng cng c lc bn cn mt ci g  mnh m hn mt cht. Khi cc khi tng ln, cc mu xut hin v vic to ni dung tr nn d dng hn, cn c cc gii php mi  lm cho ni dung phc tp d iu hng. Ch  xem danh sch (List View) l cch tt nht  chuyn gia cc lp ni dung v cc block lng nhau. V Ch  xem danh sch cung cp cho bn ci nhn tng quan v tt c cc khi trong ni dung ca bn, gi y bn c th iu hng nhanh chng n khi chnh xc m bn cn.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Cc mu  xut cho cc khi (Patterns)</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://i2.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2021/07/about-template.png\" alt=\"S dng Patterns\" width=\"437\" height=\"283\" /><figcaption>S dng Patterns</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>Bt u t phin bn ny, cng c Chuyn i mu s  xut cc mu c sn da trn block bn ang s dng. Ngay by gi, bn c th dng th trong Block Bi vit v Block Mng x hi. Khi nhiu mu c thm vo, bn s c th ly cm hng  to kiu cho trang web ca mnh m khng cn ri khi cng c chnh sa!</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">To kiu v t mu cho hnh nh</h2>\n\n\n\n<div class=\"wp-block-image\"><figure class=\"aligncenter is-resized\"><img loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\" src=\"https://i0.wp.com/wordpress.org/news/files/2021/07/about-duotone.png\" alt=\"Thm mu 2 lp vo i tng\" width=\"453\" height=\"370\" /><figcaption>Thm mu 2 lp vo i tng</figcaption></figure></div>\n\n\n\n<p>T mu cc khi hnh nh v ba ca bn bng cc b lc duotone! Duotone c th thm mu sc vo thit k ca bn v to kiu cho hnh nh ca bn (hoc video)  tch hp tt vi giao din ca bn. Bn c th ngh v hiu ng duotone nh mt b lc en trng, nhng thay v bng ti c mu en v cc im sng c mu trng, bn chn mu ca ring mnh cho bng ti v vng sng.</p>\n\n\n\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">i vi lp trnh vin</h2>\n\n\n\n<ul><li>ng k style chung v api ca giao din thng qua file <strong>theme.json</strong></li><li>Ngng h tr IE11</li><li>Thm format nh WebP</li><li>Thm mt s phn m rng ty chnh cho block</li><li>Gii thiu <a href=\"https://make.wordpress.org/core/2021/07/03/wordpress-5-8-field-guide/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">Field Guide</a></li></ul>\n\n\n\n<p><em>Bi lc dch t <a rel=\"noreferrer noopener\" href=\"https://wordpress.org/news/2021/07/tatum/\" target=\"_blank\">Gii thiu WordPress 5.8</a> Tatum bi <a href=\"https://kweb.vn/ban-cap-nhat-wordpress-5-8-co-gi-moi/\" data-type=\"URL\" data-id=\"https://kweb.vn/ban-cap-nhat-wordpress-5-8-co-gi-moi/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noreferrer noopener\">KWeb</a>.</em></p>\n\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:36:\"http://wellformedweb.org/CommentAPI/\";a:1:{s:10:\"commentRss\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:55:\"https://vi.wordpress.org/2021/07/21/wordpress-5-8/feed/\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"xml_base_explicit\";b:0;s:8:\"xml_lang\";s:0:\"\";}}}s:38:\"http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/slash/\";a:1:{s:8:\"comments\";a:1:{i:0;a:5:{s:4:\"data\";s:1:\"0\";s:7:\"attribs\";a:0:{}s:8:\"xml_base\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\