(26, 1, '2023-12-10 02:43:30', '2023-12-10 02:43:30', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Quyn bt k ny vit ra  cm n i. i  cu mang, to iu kin cho nhng hc sinh ngho nh chng ti c hc hnh n ni n chn. V sut bao nm tri i hc, ngoi my quyn sch v v mo cm bi, cuc b ln v mt on ng di hai mi cy s m trong ngi khng c mt ng xu dnh ti, th ni chi n chuyn c tin np hc ph  c i hc.<br>Quyn bt k vit ra  tng nh n qu thy c. T nhng v thy chn cht  vng qu cho n nhng bc ti cao hc rng  nc ngoi v,  em ht nhit huyt  dy d hc sinh, khng mt cht n o suy tnh hn thit. i vi h, ngh gio khng phi l ngh  lm giu m l thc hin mt s mnh. a s h  thnh ngi thin c, s cn li th lu lc bn phng. Quyn sch ny xin dnh mt khong tri  thng nh v tn knh h<br>Khi c tc phm ny, cc bn trung nin c th tm thy mt vi hnh nh ca mnh thi i hc  phi pha theo nm thng. Cc bn nghin cu c th ghi nhn c mt t chi tit ci hc mt thi  qua. Nht l cc bn tr sinh vin hc sinh khi dy trong lng mnh ch tin th, d gp bt c hon cnh kh khn gian kh no, cng c gng vt qua  tr thnh ngi hu dng</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Mt Thi n Sch', 'Tc gi: Vin Hng<br>Ngy xut bn: 11-2019<br>Kch thc: 14.5 x 20.5 cm<br>Nh xut bn: Thun Ha<br>Hnh thc ba: Ba cng<br>S trang: 430', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'mot-thoi-den-sach', '', '', '2023-12-12 03:31:24', '2023-12-12 03:31:24', '', 0, 'http://localhost/webbansach/?post_type=product&#038;p=26', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(27, 1, '2023-12-10 02:46:48', '2023-12-10 02:46:48', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>V c Sao Bin sinh nm 1947 ti Qung Nam. L nh bo, ng c trn 2000 bi bo ln nh; l nh vn, ng  c trn 50 quyn sch c xut bn; l nhc s, ng c trn 300 bi tnh ca. C cuc i ng vit trn nm triu ch.<br>V c Sao Bin c phong tng danh hiu Nhc s Sol Vng thng 08.2018. ng l nhc s Sol Vng duy nht sinh ra t t Qung Nam.<br>Gn y, ng b bnh nng, mt ting ni v dnh hu ht thi gian cho vic vit sch.<br>-o0o-<br>Si Gn - thnh ph H Ch Minh v min Nam l min t nhn hu; ng yu v ng sng. Ti  by mi hai tui; sng  min Nam c nm mi ba nm. Ti mun c vit v tm lng nhn hu, bao dung ca ngi Si Gn, ngi phng Nam.<br>Quyn sch ny khng phi l hi k. N ch ghi nhn li nhng s tht d rt nh ca ngi Si Gn, ngi min Nam dnh cho ti  qua  bn c th thy c tm lng ca h gip , yu thng, qu mn ngi phng xa n nh th no. Ngi min Nam yu s chn thnh, thng thn; ght s di tr, li dng. Gip  ai, h gip  ti ni ti chn; khng c mt iu kin g v cng khng cn ngi ta phi bo p li. Khng thch ai, h ni thng, chng ro n trnh n bao gi.<br>Ti b bnh nng, mt hn ting ni. Quyn sch ny ca ti l ting ni ca ngi tm lng ca ngi Si Gn, ngi min Nam rut tht.<br>V c Sao Bin<br>7- 2019</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Min Nam sng p', 'Tc gi: V c Sao Bin<br>Ngy xut bn: 11-2019<br>Kch thc: 13 x 20,5 cm<br>Nh xut bn: Vn Ha - Vn Ngh<br>Hnh thc ba: Ba mm<br>S trang: 120', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'mien-nam-song-dep', '', '', '2023-12-12 12:45:37', '2023-12-12 12:45:37', '', 0, 'http://localhost/webbansach/?post_type=product&#038;p=27', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(28, 1, '2023-12-10 02:49:41', '2023-12-10 02:49:41', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mt thi  nh ca Thu Trang, cu chuyn ca mt ngi tham gia hot ng ni thnh t rt sm, tng b bt, b tra tn d man v giam gi  bt Catinat v khm Ln, ri hot ng bo ch, ot vng min hoa hu Vit Nam 1955, lm din vin in nh v qua Paris ly c bng Tin s s hc ti i hc Paris 7<br>Hn Vit trn trng gii thiu li Ta ca GS L Thnh Khi v vi trch on ca hi k trong cun truyn sp xut bn ny.<br>Ta ca GS. L Thnh Khi<br>Ti quen Thu Trang gn na th k, t nhng nm cng hot ng trong Hi ngi Vit Nam yu nc  Paris, mt thi m ai cng tm nim mong ng gp phn mnh vo s nghip ginh t do, c lp cho t nc.<br>Thu y, ti khng bit qu kh ca Thu Trang v ti  min Bc, Thu Trang  min Nam thi tr.<br>Nhng sinh hot trong Hi on l dp chng ti gp nhau, bit nhau qua cc cuc hi hp, tho lun v chia cng vic. Ti ch bit qua loa v Thu Trang l mt cy bt tch cc, vn phong thuyt phc, thng xuyn vit bi ng trn cc t bo ca Hi.<br>Gn y, ti nghe Thu Trang ni ang vit Hi k v c nh  mi ti vit li Ta. Mi u ti e ngi v khng phi l nh vn, m ch l ngi thch c vn hay. Nhng khi ti c xong tp Hi k ca Thu Trang, ti  pht hin ch l mt ngi c bit. T thi tui xun, Thu Trang  dn thn khng chin,  b bt, b tra tn, nhng iu m  Paris t ai bit. Ri do thi cuc, Thu Trang  ra i  thot khi cuc sng di ch  Ng nh Dim.<br>Mt chng ng mi m ra khi Thu Trang n ng c ti Paris. Mt hoa hu thi no  Si Gn  thnh sinh vin i hc li v tr nn mt nh nghin cu S hc. C th do tm huyt cng vi tinh thn hiu hc nn Thu Trang  tm hiu v chng ng Duy Tn ca cc nh nho yu nc vo thi u th k 20, c hai khuynh hng hnh ng ca hai v Phan Bi Chu, Phan Chu Trinh. Cc v  cng tm cch chng u Ty vi chnh kh gii u Ty.<br>Tp Hi k ny theo  ti s c phn ch li cho gii c gi tr bit thm v mt vi chng ng lch s cn i ca t nc, ng thi chuyn i ca mt c nhn  gn phn no vi nhng cuc thng trm ca qu hng.<br>Ai c tp Hi k ny u s cm nhn lng yu nc ca tc gi. C nhng trang vit chn thc rt cm ng. i ba ln c chm ph bng mt vi cu th, v tc gi cn l mt nh th nn cng to c khng kh th mng khi cn thit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->',