(51, 1, '2023-12-12 03:45:51', '2023-12-12 03:45:51', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Lc con trai cn nh, ti thng c nhng tr chi  vui dnh cho con. Cc cu  thng ly ch  v thin nhin, cy ci v loi vt gn gi trong i sng hng ngy. Ti lun mong mun con c tri lng vi vn vt xung quanh mt cch du lnh v ngt ngo.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nh c ln ti hi con:  con, y l con g? Lc th c / Lc rt u/ H i u  / Mang nh i theo. Con  ngn t te sut c bui ri t hi: Sao li c con vt mang nh i theo b nh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>n khi con khng th gii  c, ti mi a ra p n, con vt l lng  chnh l c sn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Con trai ph ci, m c b th th: Con bit ri. Con c sn l con vt cn thn nht. N lo b lc nh, b v mun nn mang nh i theo lun.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ti lun mang theo trong lng cu ni ngy th ca con trai t ngy y. Ci  ngh mang nh bn mnh  khi qun, khi lc thc s qu n tng. Bi thng thng chng ta ch ngh c sn l loi vt chm chp, nn nhng ai chm, r r thng b v l chm nh sn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ngh th l oan cho c sn v thc ra chng i c rt xa. T ch l loi bn a ca vng ng Phi, c sn  c mt v sinh si  hu ht cc lc a v hi o trn th gii.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nm thng qua i, con trai b bng ngy no gi  tr thnh chng sinh vin i hc v chc con chng cn bn khon v sao c sn li mang theo nh bn mnh. Sch v chc  gip con hiu c sn l loi thn mm sng trn cn. Nu chng khng mang theo nh bn mnh th trn ng di chuyn s b cht kh bi s thay i ca mi trng.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Mi iu u c th nhn nhn di lng knh ca khoa hc. Mng thng tin ton cu gip ta d dng hiu c nhiu iu ch bng mt c nhp chut.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>y th nhng, ti vn c m mng ngh v ci cu hi ngy th ca con nm no: V sao chng ta cn phi mang theo nh bn mnh?</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>V khi y nh khng ch l ni tr chn m cn