(55, 1, '2023-12-12 03:53:25', '2023-12-12 03:53:25', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cun sch l nhng cu chuyn i sng hng ngy, nh chuyn ca nhng tm bu thip, nhng l th tay, nhng hnh phc gin d m chng ta d dng b l, c im con ngi, i sng  nhng vng min m tc gi  i qua, hay nhng cm xc ang chi phi mi ngi. T nhng tri nghim c nhn, tc gi mun chia s li nhng cm xc ca mnh v cch nhn nhn t nhng iu nh nht, n nhng quan im v cuc sng nhn sinh. Qua nhng trang vit y chn thnh ca mt ngi tr, Denley Lupin chuyn ti n ngi c nhng thng ip gi tr  yu cuc sng hn!<br>Cun sch c b cc 4 chng:</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>K nim.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Hng v cuc sng.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Tui tc.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Sng l hnh phc.<br>+TRCH ON:</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Cuc sng l mun hnh vn trng, c p c xu, c hay c d. Chng ta s ln lt c thng thc cc hng v y trong i mnh. Nu cuc sng l mt bn tic, th s c  v cay, ng, ngt, bi, chua v c nhng v k l bn chng th gi tn. Mi ngi chng ta gp, mi chuyn chng ta lm cng nh mt mu sc s gp phn vo bc tranh ghp ang dn c hon thin. Nu nh bn th nhn mi th mt cch chm ri, trm t hn, bn s cm nhn c nhng iu m trc kia bn cha bao gi ngh ti. Bn s bit thng thc cuc sng ngay c t nhng iu bn  v tnh b qua, tng khng mang nhiu  ngha vi bn. Ri bn cng s nhn ra mi ngi c mt l do ring  sng, theo  nh ca bn thn h. Khng mt ai ging bn v bn cng s khng ging mt ai khc.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Nu c t nht mt nm mt ln, hy i n mt ni m bn cha tng n trc y. Sng vi cm gic ca mt lng khch, mt ngi l, khng ai bit n, ri ri i vi thm mt du n. Nu c hy n mt ni m bn c th ngm bu tri m y sao, v ph phng tp np, nh sng nhn to  che khut ht v p ca bu tri m ng ngha, lc  ch c bn i din vi khong m bao la, t bn s nhn ra c nhiu iu  ngha v cuc sng.</li>\n<!-- /wp:list-item -->\n\n<!-- wp:list-item -->\n<li>Cho d mt ngy bn c gi i 