(57, 1, '2023-12-12 03:56:16', '2023-12-12 03:56:16', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bn thn mn! Ti cha bao gi ngh mnh s vit sch. Ti cng cha bao gi tin, mnh c th lm bnh. Ti cha bao gi bit c rng, c m li c gi tr ln lao n nh vy, cho n khi ti tht s chm tay vo Nu nh hm , trong rt nhiu nhng tht bi ca bn thn, nhng ng r, nhng con ng, rt nhiu nhng hoch nh tng lai nhng khng c li i, hay ni no m mnh tht s thuc v, nu ti b cuc, chc chn, s khng c Nhng ngy y nng, cng khng c ti ca ngy hm nay. Ti hiu cm gic ca s tht bi, chn chng, nhng ti thm tha hn rt nhiu v s kin nhn  t c c m, rng ai cng c th lm c iu mnh mun, nu bn tht s mun, v kin nh vi iu .</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nhng ngy y nng ra i, l kt qu ca rt nhiu nm ti tin tng v kin nh vi con ng mnh chn. Trong quyn sch ny, ti ghi li cng thc, kinh nghim v mong mun c chia s vi bn v tt c nhng g  tri qua trong cn bp y, vi vai tr ca mt ngi m, ngi v, ch khng phi l mt chuyn gia. Ti mong bn, nhng c gi, nhng chng trai  trt yu bp bnh, yu ci v ngt lnh ca b, ng, trng, yu cm gic bn tay lm lem bt, yu lun nhng bui chiu ma r rch v c m mnh trong cn bp nh Ti mong bn hy tin, tin vo chnh bn, rng bn hon ton c th lm c rt nhiu iu k diu.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nhng ngy y nng l nhng ngy d bn ngoi c nh th no, d l ging bo, hay l nhng bn b lo toan n mt nhoi, hay nhng vt v i thng ca cm, o, go, tin  nng ln vai th ch cn bc vo cn bp nh, c ht h v bnh thm lng t chic l c k, c thy a con b bng  i gi m cho n bnh, c sng l mnh v r rng  l chnh mnh, mt cch nguyn bn v khng h my may nghi ng v bn thn, vi ti,  tht s l nhng ngy y nng</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Ti chc bn, d ngoi tri c nh th no th trong cn nh nh m m p, ni gc bp xinh , bn s tm c nhng yu thng ngt ngo cho chnh mnh  chia s ca tc gi Hong Yn ti bn c.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trong Nhng ngy y nng tc gi Hong Yn s hng dn chng ta thc hin nhng mn bnh, cc loi mt n gin v quen thuc nh: Mt hoa qu, Crme Caramel, Oreo Cream Choux, Bnh Con S, Banana chocolate chip muffin, Vanilla Cupcake, Bnh quy b  cc bn s d dng thc hin nhng mn bnh dnh tng cho nhng ngi thng ca mnh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Nhng Ngy y Nng', 'Tc gi: Hong Yn<br>Ngy xut bn: 10-2019<br>Kch thc: 1623 cm<br>Hnh thc ba: Ba mm<br>S trang: 175', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'nhung-ngay-day-nang', '', '', '2023-12-12 03:58:17', '2023-12-12 03:58:17', '', 0, 'http://localhost/webbansach/?post_type=product&#038;p=57', 0, 'product', '', 0),
