(59, 1, '2023-12-12 03:59:01', '2023-12-12 03:59:01', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Bn c nh n ci ca mt ngi l khi bn gi ca cho h bc qua hay li cm n chn thnh t mt ngi bn khi c bn gip  khng? C phi bn cm thy hnh phc n l khi lm c iu g  cho ngi khc, d vic bn lm v cng nh b? N ci ca h c th lm bn vui c ngy, v li cm n chn thnh t ngi nhn gip bn cm thy cuc sng mnh c  ngha hn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> chnh l sc mnh t s t t - nhng vic lm nh b nhng mang n nim hnh phc to ln. Chng ta ang sng trong thi i m phn ln tin tc trn bo i, ti-vi l tiu cc, khin ta bn khon t hi c phi o c con ngi ang ngy cng i xung. Nhng d th no i na, hy lun tin rng  u  vn cn nhng con ngi t t, sng v lm iu t t mi ngy.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Sc Mnh T S T T tp hp nhng cu chuyn su sc v  ngha v s t t mi ngy. Mt hnh ng t t nh b c th to ra s khc bit ln lao cho mt ngy, thm ch l c cuc i, ca ai . Qua nhng cu chuyn trong quyn sch nh ny, bn s gp g nhng con ngi bnh d, lm nhng vic t t xut pht t tri tim ch khng mong i c n p,  ri sau  c cuc i ca h ln ngi c h gip  u thay i theo hng tt p hn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chng ti tin rng quyn sch s l dng nc mt cun tri nhng hoi nghi trong bn vn cho rng th gii ny ch y ry nhng iu xu xa. Mong rng sau khi c xong quyn sch ny, bn s n mt n ci v c thm ng lc lm iu g  t t cho ngi khc, d  ch l mt vic nh b. Nh th cng  l nim vui v vinh d ln lao cho nhng ngi thc hin quyn sch ny.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Sc Mnh Ca S T T', 'Tc gi: Jack Canfield<br>Ngy xut bn: 09-2019<br>Kch thc: 13 x 20.5 cm<br>Nh xut bn: Tng hp TP.HCM<br>Hnh thc ba: Ba mm<br>S trang: 160', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'suc-manh-cua-su-tu-te', '', '', '2023-12-12 04:00:49', '2023-12-12 04:00:49', '', 0, 'http://localhost/webbansach/?post_type=product&#038;p=59', 0, 'product', '', 0),
