(61, 1, '2023-12-12 04:00:59', '2023-12-12 04:00:59', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trong x hi c rt nhiu mi nguy. Nu chng ta t mt ngi tr vo x hi m khng tm cch bo v h, h s tip nhn nhng bo ng, cm th, s hi v bt an mi ngy, rt cuc h s b bnh. Nhng cu chuyn ca chng ta, nhng chng trnh tivi, qung co, sch bo u ti tm cc ht ging kh au ni nhng ngi tr v c nhng ngi ln. Chng ta cn mt vi nguyn tc, vi phng thuc cho cn bnh ca mnh, nhng g lnh, p v tht  c th nng ta vo.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>2.500 nm trc, Bt  a ra cc nguyn tc cho nhng ngi  t ti gia ca Ngi  gip h sng mt i sng bnh an, lnh mnh v hnh phc.  l Nm Gii v nn tng ca mi Gii ny l chnh nim. Vi chnh nim, chng ta  thc c nhng g ang xy ra ni thn th, cm th, tm hn v th gii quanh ta, cng nh ta trnh khng gy tn hi cho mnh v cho ngi.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Hc hi v thc tp theo Nm Gii v nng ta Tam Bo chc chn s mang li an lc cho bn thn, cho cng ng v cho x hi. L con ngi, chng ta cn c mt ci g  tin tng, mt ci g lnh, p v tht, mt ci g m ta c th tip xc. Trong quyn sch ny, Nm Gii c din by theo hnh thc mi,  l Bo v s sng, Hnh phc chn thc, Tnh thng ch thc, i ng v Lng nghe, Nui dng v tr liu.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Nm Gii chnh l tnh thng. Thng c ngha l hiu, bo v v mang li an vui cho i tng thng yu ca chng ta. Gii khng phi l lut l m l nhng nguyn tc hng dn gip ta tp sng nh th no  c th bo h cho mnh v cho nhng ngi xung quanh.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Khi c ngi hi: Bn c quan tm n bn thn khng?, Bn c quan tm n ngi bn i khng, Bn c quan tm n Tri t khng? cch hay nht  tr li l hnh tr Nm Gii. y l cch dy bng thn gio ch khng phi ch bng li. Nu bn tht s quan tm, xin hy hnh tr cc Gii ny  bo h cho mnh v cho mi ngi, mi loi khc na. Nu chng ta thc tp ht lng th tng lai s cn c mt cho chng ta v con chu chng</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', ' C Mt Tng Lai', 'Tc gi: Thch Nht Hnh<br>Ngy xut bn: 10-2019<br>Kch thc: 1420 cm<br>Nh xut bn: Th Gii<br>Hnh thc ba: Ba