(69, 1, '2023-12-12 04:14:34', '2023-12-12 04:14:34', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cng vi i Vit s k ton th v Khm nh Vit s thng gim cng mc, i Vit s k tin bin (VSKTB) l mt trong ba b quc s ln ca nc ta cn li n ngy nay.<br>Sau i Vit s k ton th khc in v cng b vo nm inh Su nin hiu Chnh Ho th 18, triu L Hi Tng (1697), VSKTB l b quc s th hai c khc in trong ba nm Mu Ng, K Mi, Canh Thn, hon thnh vo nm Canh Thn, nin hiu Cnh Thnh th tm (1800) triu Ty Sn.<br>B s 17 tp ny c S qun triu Ty Sn cho khc in trn c s cng trnh bin son ca s gia Ng Th S, c con ng l Ng Th Nhm tu nh, thc s l mt thnh tu quan trng v s hc ca vng triu tin b nhng qu ngn ngi y.<br>Tc gi Ng Th S (1726 - 1780) l mt nh th, nh vn, nh s hc, nh vn ho ln ca nc ta  th k XVIII, m cc tc phm cng nh cng trnh bin kho u tot ln mt tinh thn yu nc nng nn, ng thi cng th hin mt trnh  hc vn uyn bc, mt thi  tr hc nghim tc, giu tinh thn ph phn.<br>Trn phng din s hc, VSKTB cng nh Vit s tiu n ca ng u l nhng cng trnh nh vy. Con ng, Ng Th Nhm (1746 - 1803) - ngi bin tp v tu nh vn bn - l mt tri thc ln, sng sut v nhy bn,  sm tham gia phong tro Ty Sn, cng tc c lc v trung thnh vi Quang Trung Nguyn Hu, ng thi  cng hin cho vn ho nc nh nhiu cng trnh sng gi: Hn cc anh hoa, Hi Don thi vn tp, Bang giao ho thoi, Xun Thu qun kin, Trc Lm tng ch nguyn thanh VSKTB, v phng din s liu, cn bn da theo i Vit s k ton th, nhng gi tr ch yu l  nhng bnh lun sc so v nhng vn  tc gi nu ln  nh chnh hoc nh gi li.<br>T cch xp Triu  thnh \"K ngoi thuc Triu V \" n vic khng t S Nhip thnh mt k ring, khng gi S Nhip l S vng v.v.., tc gi u t r quan im c lp ca mnh. Tnh cht s lun m nt trong ngt nm trm \"li bn\" ca cc s gia ni ting i trc nh L Vn Hu, Phan Phu Tin, L Tung, Ng S Lin v ca chnh tc gi,   tot ln lng t ho dn tc v lng yu nc su sc.<br>Ngy nay c li, chng hn, on bnh lun v Hai B Trng, lp lun cht ch m sc bn, vn phong sc tch giu cht tr tnh cn khin ta xc ng v cm phc: \"Khng g kh thu phc bng nhn tm, khng g kh nm vng hn th nc. Nhng iu kh hn na l n b m tp hp c c dn chng trai trng lm ng ch. Nc ta b ni thuc  lu, s phc tng php ch ca ta  quen, ngi Trung Hoa cho l yn, rt coi thng cch cai tr ca cc quan tng h. Nhng iu on hn cht thnh g, h gt i cho l tm a tr con, thng khi ngh n chuyn ni dy th h cho l phng Nam khng phi t dng v m ngi th nht nht. Li chnh lc nh Hn va trung hng, ng o ngi ch dng, ai dm a cht thn hn mn chm vo cn tc gin ca hm beo. Th m B Trng l n b go bi cao m tc, trai trng trong nc u ci u nghe b ch huy, nhng ngi ln  nm mi my thnh cng phi nn hi khng dm tri lnh. Lu Vn tng dit c qun hng, chng ni i ch, li c quyn hp binh sai tng, cp  xe thuyn lng thc, th m phi n tra ng mun, dc c vo vic c mu. M Phc Ba tng lm c nc Tin Linh, ph tan t Tam Lang mt cch d dng, th m khi sang ng n  Lng Bc phi nu qun g nga i chm, giu xe di chm, bng lo ru ngay ngy, ming ni nng d dt. Ting tm ca Hai B chn ng c Di H, c nghip ca Hai B dc ngang khp tri. i, anh hng qu!\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'i Vit S K Tin Bin', 'Tc gi: Nhiu Tc Gi<br>Ngy xut bn: 10-2018<br>Kch thc: 16 x 24 cm<br>Nh xut bn: Hng c<br>Hnh thc ba: Ba cng<br>S trang: 776', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'dai-viet-su-ky-tien-bien', '', '', '2023-12-12 05:16:38', '2023-12-12 05:16:38', '', 0, 'http://localhost/webbansach/?post_type=product&#038;p=69', 0, 'product', '', 0),
(70, 1, '2023-12-12 04:15:43', '2023-12-12 04:15:43', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Trong hnh trnh tm li v truyn gi nhng tc phm tiu biu ca nn vn hc nc nh, NXB Kim ng c bit ch  n Lnh Nam Chch Qui. Son gi V Qunh - mt trong hai ngi ghi chp li nhng truyn trong Lnh Nam chch qui lit truyn ni rng, khi chp xong truyn ny, ng  ngi m ly m c. iu  chng t c sc hp dn c bit ca tc phm. Trong ln xut bn ny, NXB Kim ng mong mun gi li gn nguyn vn ni dung tc phm ca cc tc gi qua bn dch ca hc gi inh Gia Khnh v Nguyn Ngc San.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p> Lnh Nam Chch Qui c nhiu truyn mang nhng t tng, tnh cm rt phng khong. Qu y l tm gng phn chiu i sng tinh thn  mt thi k m mi quan h o l gia ngi vi ngi cn ci m, cha b nhng khun so, tn iu g b qu cht ch. Li c nhng truyn chu s hn ch ca  thc h phong kin, nht l cc truyn do cc son gi i sau thm vo. Song nhn chung, ton b tp truyn vn thm nhun mt tinh thn nhn o ch ngha ca vn hc dn gian. C th t nhiu thy c   thi  yu ght ca nhn dn: yu chnh ngha, ght phi ngha, yu iu thin, ght iu c,  cao nhng mi quan h tt p thy chung gia ngi vi ngi.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>c bit hn c, bn ang cm trn tay n bn Lnh Nam chch qui u tin v duy nht  Vit Nam c tranh minh ha mu p, c v l.  l sn phm ca qu trnh sng to khng ngng ngh trong sut thi gian di ca ha s T Huy Long, xut pht t ngun cm hng c bit vi tc phm Lnh Nam chch qui, v t mong mun ca NXB Kim ng a mt n phm c o ti tay bn c. Vi nhng tm huyt nh vy, hi vng bn c s thm hiu v yu qu, trn trng nhng di sn m ng cha  li cho chng ta.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'Lnh Nam Chch Qui', 'Tc gi: Trn Th Php<br>Ngy xut bn: 08-2019<br>Kch thc: 24 x 32 cm<br>Nh xut bn: Kim ng<br>Hnh thc ba: Ba cng<br>S trang: 260', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'linh-nam-chich-quai', '', '', '2023-12-12 04:19:19', '2023-12-12 04:19:19', '', 0, 'http://localhost/webbansach/?post_type=product&#038;p=70', 0, 'product', '', 0),
