(72, 1, '2023-12-12 04:20:08', '2023-12-12 04:20:08', '<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>La Sn phu t, tc v phu t t La Sn, l nh Nho ni ting ca i Vit th k XVIII-XIX. Cng vi Tuyt Giang phu t Nguyn Bnh Khim, hai c c suy tn l phu t (nh hin trit). La Sn phu t h Nguyn, hy Minh, t Quang Thip. Nhng i cha Trnh Doanh, ch Quang l quc hy, cho nn lc i thi, c phi b ch m (ch lt) y, v ly tn Nguyn Thip. Ngy sau, trong cc sch v vn kin cng u chp nh vy. Sau , c li ly mt t khc l Khi Xuyn, nht l trong cc th tr li cho vua Quang Trung Nguyn Hu.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chuyn kho v nhn vt lch s La Sn phu t c Gio s Hong Xun Hn su tm t liu t nhng nm 1939,  trch ng vi k trn bo Thanh Ngh t nm 1944-1945. Gio s Hong Xun Hn  tr tnh em in thnh sch nhng Cch mng thng Tm 1945 n ra nn k hoch in tm hon. Nm 1949, ng cho ra mt bn c mt chuyn kho c o v nhn vt lch s L Thng Kit (Sng Nh, H Ni) m trc-sau cha c cng trnh no vt qua. Mi n nm 1952, sau khi gia nh ng sang Paris (Php) nh c, La Sn phu t mi chnh thc ra mt bn c (Minh Tn, Paris xut bn).</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Cuc i La Sn phu t trong cun sch cng tn c Gio s Hong Xun Hn phc dng rt chi tit, qua nhng kho cu t liu cng phu, bn c s nhn thy rt r hnh trng ca nhn vt lch s sng cch chng ta hn 200 nm. Tm vc v nhn cch ca v phu t t La Sn, thi  ca ngi tr thc trc thi cuc thng qua l xut x c Gio s Hong Xun Hn m t rt r thng qua mi quan h ca c vi v anh hng o vi Quang Trung Nguyn Hu. Nguyn Hu ba ln gi th mi, ba ln La Sn phu t t chi. Nguyn Hu lc u trong mt La Sn phu t ch l mt thng gic nc ngoi, sau li thnh mt gian hng mn k dit Trnh ph L, ri thn hoch nc mnh. Trong khi , La Sn phu t l ti ca nh L, mc nhin cng nhn ci mt tri chnh ng ca nh L. Qua th t, qua thi  cu hin ca Nguyn Hu, v qua s kin L Chiu Thng a gic vo Thng Long, Nguyn Hu xng vng ko qun ra Bc nh tan qun Thanh, t tng ca La Sn phu t  c nhng chuyn bin quan trng: chu gp mt, hin k nh gic, ra hp tc vi Quang Trung qua vic dch sch, gi th khuyn vua La Sn phu t chu chp nhn quy lut hng vong, l thnh suy  i; c chp nhn thc t l nh L ht vn; c chp nhn Nguyn Hu l bc trng phu C chu ra hp tc nhng rt c chng mc.<br>Chuyn La Sn phu t l chuyn mt c nhn c bit, mt c tnh c bit.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>\"Ch khen mt c nhn nh vy l quyn bnh lun ca mi ngi. Khng i chng ta, nhng k ng thi cng  tng c tn dng hay kch bc. Nhng chng ta nay khng cn  trong mt x hi m t t tng n hnh ng ton da vo o Nho. Vy xt on La Sn phu t c phn d khch quan hn. Nhng mun hiu tm l phu t, ta phi t t mnh vo khong lch s hn n bc nht  nc ta, l khong t cui L n u Nguyn.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>V chng, ci thi  v vi ca c nhn kia cha hn  hon ton v hiu. Tuy khng gi mt vai quan trng g i vi thi cuc, nhng bi ci c tnh ca mnh, phu t  lin can n tt c cc vai chnh trong mn lch s ng thi.\"</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->', 'La Sn Phu T', 'Tc gi: Hong Xun Hn<br>Ngy xut bn: 03-2016<br>Kch thc: 15.5 x 23 cm<br>Nh xut bn: Khoa hc x hi<br>Hnh thc ba: Ba mm<br>S trang: 301', 'publish', 'open', 'closed', '', 'la-son-phu-tu', '', '', '2023-12-12 05:18:05', '2023-12-12 05:18:05', '', 0, 'http://localhost/webbansach/?post_type=product&#038;p=72', 0, 'product', '', 0),
